span>.</span></font></font></font></p>\r\n								<p style="margin-bottom: 0.5cm;">\r\n									<font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">A <span>chaque</span> <span>cr&eacute;dit</span> <span>arbre</span> <span>gagn&eacute;</span> par <span>vos</span> <span>filleuls</span> <strong><span>vous</span> <span>accumulez</span> 10 % de <span>leurs</span> gains en <span>cr&eacute;dits</span> <span>arbres</span> </strong><span>que</span> <span>vous</span> <span>pourrez</span> <span>ensuite</span> planter via la <span>plate-forme</span> de reforestation !</font></font></font></p>\r\n								<p style="margin-bottom: 0.5cm">\r\n									<font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span>N&#39;h&eacute;sitez</span> <span>donc</span> pas a faire <span>conna&icirc;tre</span> <span>Up2green</span> a <span>votre</span> <span>famille</span> et a <span>vos</span> <span>amis</span> !</font></font></font></p>\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td style="border-left: #ddd 1px solid; vertical-align: top width: 50%;">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong><font color="#008000"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><font size="3"><span>Faites</span> <span>d&eacute;couvrir</span> <span>up2green</span> en <span>offrant</span> un coupon de plantation <span>&agrave;</span> <span>votre</span> <span>famille</span> et <span>&agrave;</span> <span>vos</span> <span>amis</span> !</font></font></font></strong></p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<span>Vous</span> <span>voulez</span> faire <strong>un <span>cadeau</span> <span>ou</span> <span>une</span> surprise unique</strong> a <span>l&#39;un</span> de <span>vos</span> <span>proches</span> ?</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<span>Alors</span> <span>pourquoi</span> ne pas <span>lui</span> <strong><span>offrir</span> des <span>arbres</span> <span>&agrave;</span> planter <span>sur</span> la <span>Plan&egra