							<span>Vous</span> <span>avez</span>&nbsp;<span>&eacute;galement</span> la <span>possibilit&eacute;</span> de <span>voir</span> la <span>capacit&eacute;</span> de plantation des <span>programmes</span> <span>afin</span> de <span>pouvoir</span> <span>juger</span> par <span>vous</span> <span>m&ecirc;me</span> de <span>l&#39;avancement</span> des plantations et de <span>voir</span> les <span>programmes</span> qui <span>ont</span> le plus <span>besoin</span> de&nbsp;<span>vous</span>.</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td style="border-left: #ddd 1px solid; vertical-align: top">\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong><font color="#008000"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><font size="3"><span><span>Up2green</span></span> <span><span>s&#39;enrichit</span></span> <span><span>d&#39;un</span></span> module de <span><span>paiement</span></span> via <span><span>Paypal</span></span> !</font></font></font></strong></p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<span><span>Maintenant</span></span> <span><span>vous</span></span> <span><span>pouvez</span></span> <span><span>participer</span></span> encore plus <span><span>activement</span></span> <span><span>&agrave;</span></span> la reforestation en <span><span>cr&eacute;ditant</span></span> <span><span>votre</span></span> <span><span>compte</span></span> en <span><span>arbres</span></span> via <span><span>Paypal</span></span> (<span><span>d&#39;autres</span></span> modes <span><span>d&#39;achat</span></span> <span><span>disponibles</span></span> <span><span>bient&ocirc;t</span></span>).</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<strong><span>D&egrave;s</span> <span><span>maintenant</span></span> <span><span>vous</span></span> <span><span>pouvez</span></span> <span>acheter</span> <span>directement</span> des <span><span>cr&eacute;dits</span></span> <span><span>arbres</span></span> via <span><span>Paypal</span></span></strong> et les planter <span><span>sur</span></span> la <span><span>parcelle</span></span> de <span><span>votre</span></span> <span>choix</span> ! Les <span><span>cr&eacute;dits</span></span> <span><span>arbres</span></span> <span>achet&eacute;s</span> via <span><span>Paypal</span></span> <span>sont</span> <span>identiques</span> aux <span><span>cr&eacute;dits</span></span> <span><span>arbres</span></span> <span>accumul&eacute;s</span> <span>gratuitement</span>&nbsp;<span>lors</span> de <span><span>vos</span></span> <span><span>recherches</span></span> <span><span>sur</span></span> <span><span>Up2green</span></span>. <span><span>Vous</span></span> <span><span>pouvez</span></span> <span><span>ensuite</span></span> les planter via la <span>plateforme</span> de reforestation <span>dans</span> le <span><span>programme</span></span> de <span><span>votre</span></span> <span>choix</span>.</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td colspan="2" style="vertical-align: top">\r\n								<p style="margin-bottom: 0.5cm">\r\n									<strong><font color="#4b0082"><font size="3">Partenaires, pour <span>vous</span> <span>aussi</span> le plein de <span>nouveaut&eacute;s</span> !</font></font></strong></p>\r\n								<p style="margin-bottom: 0.5cm">\r\n									<span>Up2green</span> travaille <span>activement</span> pour <span>que</span> <span>vous</span> puissiez accompagner <span>vos</span> utilisateurs dans leur actes de reforestation ! <span>Vous</span> <span>pouvez</span> d&eacute;sormais <span>mieux</span> g&eacute;rer <span>vos</span> coupons dans la section &quot;Mes coupons&quot; de <span>votre</span> profil et exporter les donn&eacute;es si <span>vous</span> en <span>avez</span> <span>besoin</span>.</p>\r\n								<p style="margin-bottom: 0.5cm">\r\n									<span>Nous</span> travaillons <span>actuellement</span> pour <span>pouvoir</span> <span>vous</span> permettre de modifier simplement <span>votre</span> logo, <span>votre</span> accroche et <span>&eacute;galement</span> <span>vous</span> permettre de cr&eacute;er <span>votre</span> page personnalis&eacute;e pour <span>vos</span> visiteurs !</p>\r\n								<p style="margin-bottom: 0.5cm">\r\n									Suivez l&#39;actualit&eacute; de l&#39;Association <span>Up2green</span> Reforestation, <span>ces</span> nouvelles fonctionnalit&eacute;s approchent !</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<table style="width: 100%;">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style="width: 100%;">\r\n								<ul>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<span style="font-size:12px;"><strong><a href="http://association.up2green.com/article/nos_objectifs"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">Qui sommes <span>nous</span> ?</span></a></strong></span></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<span style="font-size:12px;"><strong><a href="http://reforestation.up2green.com/"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">Plantez un <span>arbre</span> !</span></a></strong></span></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<span style="font-size:12px;"><strong><a href="http://up2green.com/checkout/coupon"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);"><span>Offrez</span> un arbe !</span></a></strong></span></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<span style="font-size:12px;"><strong><a href="http://up2green.com/checkout/credit"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">Aidez l&#39;association</span></a></strong></span></li>\r\n								</ul>\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td>\r\n								<img src="../../../images/newsletter/footer-plante.gif" /></td>\r\n							<td>\r\n								<table cellpadding="15" cellspacing="0" height="220" style="background: url(/images/newsletter/footer-right.jpg) no-repeat transparent" width="280">\r\n									<tbody>\r\n										<tr>\r\n											<td style="text-align: right; height: 80px;">\r\n												<a href="http://association.up2green.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#008000;"><span style="font-size: 11px;"><strong>Le blog de l&#39;association</strong></span></span></a></td>\r\n										</tr>\r\n										<tr>\r\n											<td style="text-align: right; height: 70px;">\r\n												<a href="http://www.up2green.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#008000;"><span style="font-size: 11px;"><strong>Le <span>moteur</span> de <span>recherche</span></strong></span></span></a></td>\r\n										</tr>\r\n										<tr>\r\n											<td style="text-align: right;">\r\n												<p>\r\n													<a href="http://reforestation.up2green.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#008000;"><span style="font-size: 11px;"><strong>plateforme de reforestation</strong></span></span></a></p>\r\n											</td>\r\n										</tr>\r\n									</tbody>\r\n								</table>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n				<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n					<span style="color:#8e7766;"><span style="font-size: 9px;">Conform&eacute;ment <span>&agrave;</span> la loi Informatique et Libert&eacute; du 6 janvier 1978, <span>vous</span> disposez <span>d&#39;un</span> droit d&#39;acc&egrave;s, de rectification et de suppression des informations <span>vous</span> concernant. Si <span>vous</span> ne souhaites plus recevoir nos informations, merci de modificier les param&egrave;tres de <span>votre</span> <span>compte</span> <a href="http://up2green.com/user/profil">ici</a> <span>ou</span> d&#39;envoyer un e-mail <span>&agrave;</span> <a href="mailto:webmaster@up2green.com?subject=D%C3%A9sinscription"><span>webmaster@up2green.com</span></a></span></span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n					<span style="color:#8e7766;"><span style="font-size: 9px;">Association <span><span><span><span><span>Up2green</span></span></span></span></span> Reforestation - 38 rue <span><span><span><span>Desaix</span></span></span></span> 75015 Paris - FRANCE</span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 'en', 'newsletter-1');
